address.streetAddress: The Fletcher F Plan, Wendell Falls

location.fullValue: The Fletcher F Plan, Wendell Falls

data.description: Lovely Brick and Vinyl home on a corner lot with fenced in backyard, in much desired Edgemont Landing.  Home have large open kitchen with lots of counterspace and walk-in pantry with handmade wood barn doors.  Eat-in Kitchen area opens to private fenced in yard with patio.  Living room is open with a lot of natural light and has fireplace.  Front room could be Formal living or Home office space.  Separate dining room. Huge Bonus room is multi purpose.  Large Owner Suite has 2 walk in closets and attach bath with Garden tub and walk in shower.
